Yedoma_IRYP	Yedoma distribution areas with confidence classes	Circum-Arctic, from about 50¡ N			We merged the units interpreted as Yedoma into a single data layer across multiple map tiles. We implemented a Yedoma confidence classification based on source details and additional information from other feature classes of this IRYP dataset.			IPA Yedoma Action Group	IRYP_v2_yedoma_confidence_Shapefile.zip	ZIP	IRYP_v2_yedoma_confidence_Shapefile.zip
Yedoma_IRYP	IRYP v2 yedoma domain Shapefile, extent of the Yedoma domain	Circum-Arctic, from about 50¡ N			Using a spatial buffer of 20 km around mapped Yedoma occurrences, we derived an extent of the Yedoma domain. Our result is a vector-based map of the current pan-Arctic Yedoma domain.			IPA Yedoma Action Group	IRYP_v2_yedoma_domain_Shapefile.zip	ZIP	IRYP_v2_yedoma_domain_Shapefile.zip
Yedoma_IRYP	IRYP v2 field sites Shapefile, sites of literature data on Yedoma characteristics	Circum-Arctic, from about 50¡ N			This feature includes available literature data on Yedoma characteristics concerning occurence and thickness.			IPA Yedoma Action Group	IRYP_v2_field_sites_Shapefile.zip	ZIP	IRYP_v2_field_sites_Shapefile.zip
Yedoma_IRYP	IRYP v2 map sources Shapefile, extents and sources of map data	Circum-Arctic, from about 50¡ N			This layer contains the extents and sources of the integrated map data.			IPA Yedoma Action Group	IRYP_v2_map_sources_Shapefile.zip	ZIP	IRYP_v2_map_sources_Shapefile.zip
Yedoma_IRYP	IRYP v2 as Esri FileGDB	Circum-Arctic, from about 50¡ N			This file includes the IRYP v2 layer field sites, yedoma confidence, yedoma domain and map sources as Esri FileGDB feature classes.			IPA Yedoma Action Group	IRYP_v2_FileGDB.zip	ZIP	IRYP_v2_FileGDB.zip
Yedoma_IRYP	IRYP v2 field photos Shapefile, point feature class of photos showing Yedoma	Circum-Arctic, from about 50¡ N			For Yedoma ground truthing as an additional visualisation opportunity we initiate a Yedoma photo database. This point feature class includes the spatial location of photos showing Yedoma taken by several members of the IPA Yedoma Action Group.			IPA Yedoma Action Group	IRYP_v2_field_photos_Shapefile.zip	ZIP	IRYP_v2_field_photos_Shapefile.zip
